Zero point energy                ...      0.24819927 Eh     155.75 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.01047765 Eh       6.57 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
